            <install-description>
                <alert level="info">
                    Please contact us if you wish to port Sonarr v3 for any other distribution that the ones already listed.<br/>
                    Sonarr v2 is supported by various third-parties on other platforms and we prefer to coordinate the port of v3.
                </alert>

                <p>
                    A generic download is available for linux, but dependencies, installation and permissions will need to be done manually.
                </p>

                <a class="btn btn-sonarr" href="//services.sonarr.tv/v1/download/main/latest?version=3&os=linux">Download Linux .tar.gz</a>
            </install-description>
        </tabview-pane>
